### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Assigner un prestataire (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assign-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_service_id": "event-service-uuid-here",
  "provider_id": "provider-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Erreur: event_service_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assign-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_id": "provider-uuid-here"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: provider_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assign-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_service_id": "event-service-uuid-here"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: prestataire incompatible
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assign-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_service_id": "event-service-traiteur-uuid",
  "provider_id": "provider-decoration-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: accès non autorisé
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assign-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_service_id": "event-service-uuid-here",
  "provider_id": "provider-uuid-here"
}

